Jacqueline Fernandez Is One Beautiful Actress And These Pictures Are Proof
Jacqueline Fernandez is one of the popular actresses in Bollywood. Her father is a Sri Lankan while mother is a Malaysian national. She finished her schooling in Bahrain after herarents moved there. She studied Media and Communications in Sydney after completing her schooling. She was crowned the Miss Sri Lanka in 2006. After her triumph, she started her television career anchoring a Sri Lanka show on business called Lanka Business Report.
She made her Bollywood debut with the movie Aladin (2009) which was helmed by Sujoy Ghosh with stars like Amitabh Bachchan, Sanjay Dutt and Riteish Deshmukh. She hogged the limelight with the thriller Murder 2 (2011). After this, she has done several glamourous roles in her kitty. Housefull 2 (2012), Race 2 (2013), Kick (2014), Housefull 3 (2016) and Judwaa 2 (2017) are few of her popular Bollywood films.

description: Jacqueline Fernandez is a Bahraini-born-sri lankan-Indian actress, former model, and the winner of the Miss Universe Sri Lanka pageant of 2006. In 2009 she started her career in Bollywood with the movie Aladin and since then has made a place in Bollywood. Jacqueline Fernandez was crowned Miss Universe Sri Lanka in 2006, and represented her country at Miss Universe 2006.
